snippet.title: Episode 10: How do you say "it's not working" without saying "it's not working"?
snippet.description:
During today's episode, Amber and Joe discuss the recent tragic Colorado wildfires and the potential for a narrative change from C-vid to climate change. We touch on AOC and her epic, maskless vacation in Florida, and then talk about continuous booster mandates in the United States and around the world. Finally, we discuss the media messaging that's basically admitting their medicine doesn't work without directly stating that it doesn't work, with and in depth look at the CDC new guidance for cruise ships.



Articles Mentioned:

ZeroHedge: Monday January 3rd: Life Insurance CEO Says Deaths Up 40% Among Those Aged 18-64

ZeroHedge: Monday January 3rd: FDA Approves Pfizer Booster for 12-15 Year Olds

Daily Sabah: Friday December 31st: Turkey Starts Offering 5th Dose of COVID-19 Booster Shots

Boriquagato Substack: Sunday January 2nd: Moving The Goalposts Is The New Settled Science

CNBC : Thursday December 30th: U.S. CDC says people should ‘avoid cruise travel, regardless of vaccination status’
